<messaging:emailTemplate subject="G&H Receive Request for {!RelatedTo.ASI_GnH_Applicant__r.Name} - Return request (#{!RelatedTo.Name})" recipientType="User" relatedToType="ASI_GnH_Request__c"><messaging:htmlEmailBody ><html><body>    <p>                Please note the following G&amp;H Request status - Return request.<br />        G&amp;H 요청 상태 - 반환 요망    </p>    <table>            <tr>                <td>G&amp;H Request No (요청 번호)</td>                <td>: &nbsp; {!RelatedTo.Name}</td>            </tr>            <tr>                <td>Applicant Name (신청자 성명)</td>                <td>: &nbsp; {!RelatedTo.ASI_GnH_Applicant__r.Name}</td>            </tr>            <tr>                <td>Department (부서)</td>                <td>: &nbsp; {!RelatedTo.ASI_GnH_Department__c}</td>            </tr>            <tr>                <td>G&amp;H Type (G&amp;H 유형)</td>                <td>: &nbsp; {!RelatedTo.ASI_GnH_Type__c}</td>            </tr>            <tr>                <td>Receiving date (수령 날짜)</td>                <td>: &nbsp; <apex:outputText value="{0, date, yyyy'-'MMM'-'d}">                                <apex:param value="{!RelatedTo.ASI_GnH_Benefit_Date__c}" />                            </apex:outputText>                </td>            </tr>            <tr>                <td>Name of Donor (제공한 사람의 이름)</td>                <td>: &nbsp; {!RelatedTo.ASI_GnH_Offeror__r.Name}</td>            </tr>            <tr>                <td>Organization of Donor (제공한 사람의 회사/조직)</td>                <td>: &nbsp; {!RelatedTo.ASI_GnH_Offeror_Organization__c}</td>            </tr>            <tr>                <td>Estimated Amount per Recipient (수령인 당 추정 금액)</td>                <td>: &nbsp; <apex:outputText value="{0, number, ###,###,###,###.##}">                                <apex:param value="{!RelatedTo.ASI_GnH_Amount_per_Recipient__c}" />                            </apex:outputText>                </td>            </tr>            <tr>                <td>PAX (총 인원)</td>                <td>: &nbsp; <apex:outputText value="{0, number, ###,###,###,###}">                                <apex:param value="{!RelatedTo.ASI_GnH_PAX__c}" />                            </apex:outputText>                </td>            </tr>            <tr>                <td>Purpose (목적)</td>                <td>: &nbsp; {!RelatedTo.ASI_GnH_Purpose__c}</td>            </tr>    </table>    <p>You can click this&nbsp;<apex:outputLink value="{!LEFT($Api.Partner_Server_URL_140, FIND('.com/',$Api.Partner_Server_URL_140)+3)}/{!RelatedTo.id}">link</apex:outputLink> to access the G&amp;H Request for details.<br/>       본 링크를 클릭하시면 G&amp;H요청에 관한 세부 사항을 확인할 수 있습니다.</p></body></html></messaging:htmlEmailBody></messaging:emailTemplate>